{"id":"8970","user":{"id":"101860","nickname":"四片叶de三叶吖","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FqcR23gyTBxqpGDVypZpJe8hw4uq","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【少院士讲堂】第十课！—BOX2.0课程倒计时；第三弹：亭，妙不可言~","content":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fldpr7vYkiT_baiInfGYqSfBkhPe\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font size=\"4\">&nbsp;++++ 本节目由：无限卡崩的谷歌，史上最渣的电脑，赞助提供++++</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\"><br></font></p>\n<p>　hello ！我是尚冲，快要考试了呢。在最后一期，我想讲一下亭子的建造这次不只有中式欧~　　</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>　　　<img src=\"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/70cFvHSh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=1706582198,3172543832&amp;fm=27&amp;gp=0.jpg\"><img src=\"https://ss3.bdstatic.com/70cFv8Sh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=3242682090,3968150041&amp;fm=27&amp;gp=0.jpg\"><br></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ss2.bdstatic.com/70cFvnSh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=153788236,984264964&amp;fm=27&amp;gp=0.jpg\"><img><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">（此图不裂~此图不裂~此图不裂~）</font><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font size=\"7\">+++<font color=\"#0000ff\">正文</font>+++</font></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font size=\"6\">&amp;tíng</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"7\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;亭</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"6\">&nbsp; 基本知识</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; <font size=\"4\">&nbsp;亭：</font><img></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 是一种中国传统建筑，源于周代。多建于路旁，供行人休息、乘凉或观景用。亭一般为开敞性结构，没有围墙，顶部可分为六角、八角、圆形等多种形状，中式亭子多为多角亭，欧式则多为半圆穹顶。图片在上</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<font size=\"4\"> 历史：</font><img src=\"https://ss3.bdstatic.com/70cFv8Sh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=2050238122,2538638655&amp;fm=27&amp;gp=0.jpg\"></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 亭的历史十分悠久，但古代最早的亭并不是供观赏用的建筑。周代的亭，是设在边防要塞的小堡垒， 到了秦汉，亭的建筑扩大到各地，成为地方维护治安的基层组织所使用。</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 魏晋南北朝时，代替亭制而起的是驿。之后，亭和驿逐渐废弃。但民间却有在交通要道筑亭为旅途歇息之用的习俗，因而沿用下来。也有的作为迎宾送客的礼仪场所。同时，亭作为点景建筑，开始出现园林之中。&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 到了隋唐时期，园苑之中筑亭已很普遍，如杨广在洛阳兴建的西苑中就有风亭月观等景观建筑。</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; &nbsp;宋代有记载的亭子就更多了，建筑也极精巧。在宋《营造法式》中就详细地描述了多种亭的形状和建造技术，此后，亭的建筑便愈来愈多，形式也多种多样。&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"6\">so......</font><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Ft7DBzYt02sbZf7QJ80Jk-ejQhwI\"></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <font size=\"6\">建造方不方</font></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">中式亭子</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">关键：地基，石木，屋顶</font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;台基是很重要的</p>\n<p>&nbsp; 以下是三种建筑中比较常见的</p>\n<p>四方地基 ，手动滑稽（咦？好押韵）</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FiiFZRTFQn7x-5lIdmVi8cUoHx0v\"><br></p>\n<p>八边地基</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgG9BfPDRJjeSWgxs6PuUXfumaVk\"><br></p>\n<p>圆形双层 地基（这个圆形不太圆）</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FhjwvjKDC-U5Y4RjQyqwl57a2LQX\"><br></p>\n<p>正式建造</p>\n<p>作者使用的是圆形地基+八柱</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgiAtAERdqsUUTacqWF-3K0dNVEI\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FvDvRW5ZI7KaCYCbTAkqrt1ITaZE\"></p>\n<p>围栏围栏</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fgk3r03BkhEhe19TZOzYaPW_DJj8\"><br></p>\n<p>默默地四角攒尖&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FmZrTE-DlY_jUSTeCOnVC0rik88B\"></p>\n<p>上瓦而生</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FiKgrIy9lT5n5Jh_gCCBm_YUN4NM\"><br></p>\n<p>上瓦x2</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FuwRuZZqgiUF7VFM0-2N0TlakydO\"><br></p>\n<p>当当！</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FplOunE9uyPEem589iQV00kuknSa\"><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"5\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">欧式亭子</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">关键：大理石（石英），穹顶，白色</font></p>\n<p>地基走起</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FqKNWemO7Iq8xB5Ql3yaD53jrkyE\"><br></p>\n<p>柱子</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FjD8gbpLLL6OFQl890ttFy7VnKLq\"></p>\n<p>一圈圆形<br></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FiAOF2x6fAoGdwm4kU_thHxPAHdP\"></p>\n<p>往上成半圆</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FvhdjSXydYk5zPHnifX7fkBYpVjQ\"></p>\n<p>盖上玻璃，+修饰</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Ft7aYRlSEgLOlL9YeWd6j9-K7Aj0\"><br></p>\n<p>当x2</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fmpaw9svmis4XiPLNM3W__bL2sj9\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"6\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; THANK FOR YOUR ALL READING~~</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"6\">HAVE A GOOD TIME!</font></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/emoji/codemao/4.gif\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/emoji/codemao/4.gif\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/emoji/codemao/4.gif\"><iframe frameborder=\"no\" width=\"330\" height=\"86\" src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&amp;id=28830410&amp;auto=1&amp;height=66\"></iframe><font size=\"6\"><br></font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>","board_id":"2","board_name":"积木编程乐园","updated_at":1517362503,"created_at":1517127134,"n_views":529,"n_replies":9,"n_comments":0,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":true,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}